I can normally play for a very long time without buying food as I linked my forage button to my left turn key, every time I turn, I attempt forage. Also link Sense heading to right turn key till its maxed then swap it for detect traps, maxed both of those.<br>
Forage is a good skill to have in places far away from civilization, such as LOIO (great if you want poison tho).<br>
